Controlling  and containing epidemics is an important healthcare challenge worldwide. Nowadays people easily can move from different countries, leading that human fluxes are coming increasingly complex and heterogeneous, it makes easier the propagations of pathogens.In this scenario, approaches that can surveille subpopulations movement are critical for enhancing containment and mitigation processes. Modeling epidemic diffusion 






